  "text": "Posterior to PPC, labelling in area AM was contained entirely in V2M (following the nomenclature of [CITATION_1] , and area RL continued to straddle the architectonic boundary between V2L and S1 barrels ( Figure 3E ). Even more caudally, at approximately -2.87mm posterior to bregma, labeling in PM overlapped completely with 1 0",
